text:
I don't sure that you need to use converters in low level API -- that may clash with high level one.
I'm +0 for removing conversions but the final decision if up to you, sure.
title: Type convertors

text:
Just to be clear this mentions [aioredis/util.py _converters](https://github.com/popravich/aioredis/blob/master/aioredis/util.py#L4)

This convertors are for internal use only.
There will be other interface for customizing type convertion, some day.
